title: At least two dead in school bus highway accident
text:
At least two dead in school bus highway accident 11:53am BST - 00:58
At least two people, one student and one teacher, were killed in a highway collision between a school bus and a dump truck. More than forty others were injured. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
